  <brief_title>Bilateral vs. Unilateral Erector Spinae Plane Block</brief_title>
  <official_title>Bilateral vs. Unilateral Erector Spinae Plane Block for Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy; A Randomised Controlled Trial</official_title>
